description: It is the first time the annual show of Russian patriotism is postponed, a blow to President Putin.
title: Coronavirus: Putin postpones Russia's WW2 victory parade
title_page: Coronavirus: Putin postpones Russia's WW2 victory parade - BBC News
maintext: Mr Putin told his Security Council the "risks associated with the epidemic, whose peak has not passed yet, are extremely high", and "this does not give me the right to begin preparations for the parade and other mass events now".
